  <entry>
    <title>D-Link DIR-645 固件分析</title>
    <url>/cyber-security/vulnerability/app/d-link/d-link_dir-645_%E5%9B%BA%E4%BB%B6%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>通过 D-Link 资源站点下载 <a href="https://files.dlink.com.au/products/DIR-645/REV_A/Firmware/DIR645_FW103B11/DIR645A1_FW103B11.zip">A1 1.03B11</a> 版本的固件镜像。</p>
<span id="more"></span>

<h2 id="固件解压"><a href="#固件解压" class="headerlink" title="固件解压"></a>固件解压</h2><p>使用 Binwalk 进行固件解压。</p>
<figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">binwalk -Me DIR645A1_FW103B11.bin</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="固件仿真"><a href="#固件仿真" class="headerlink" title="固件仿真"></a>固件仿真</h2><p>使用 FirmAE 进行固件仿真。</p>
<figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cd ./FirmAE</span><br><span class="line">./init.sh</span><br><span class="line">sudo ./run.sh -c DIR645 ./DIR645A1_FW103B11.bin</span><br><span class="line">sudo ./run.sh -d DIR645 ./DIR645A1_FW103B11.bin</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>通过 <code>http://192.168.0.1</code> 访问路由器登录界面，使用默认账户 <code>Admin / &lt;空&gt;</code> 可以进行登录。</p>
<p><img src="%E8%AE%BF%E9%97%AE%E7%99%BB%E5%BD%95%E7%95%8C%E9%9D%A2.png" alt="访问登录界面"></p>
<h2 id="参考链接"><a href="#参考链接" class="headerlink" title="参考链接"></a>参考链接</h2><p><a href="https://files.dlink.com.au/products/DIR-645/REV_A/Firmware/">files.dlink.com.au - &#x2F;products&#x2F;DIR-645&#x2F;REV_A&#x2F;Firmware&#x2F;</a></p>
]]></content>
